Pass condition in format: function(metric, value). 
Functions: less_than, greater_than, less_than_eq, greater_than_eq. 
Metrics: avg, p90, p95, p99, error_rate, rps. 
Example: less_than(p95, 500) or less_than(error_rate, 5)

.TP Examples:

Examples:
